<html>

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<title>Security Alert</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; color: #333;">
	<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
		style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
		<tr>
			<td>
				<h2 style="color: #d93025;">Unusual Login Attempt Detected</h2>

				<p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>

				<p>
					We noticed a sign-in attempt to your account from a new device in
					<strong>{{location}}</strong>
					on
					<strong>{{today}}</strong>.
				</p>

				<p>If this was you, no further action is needed.</p>

				<p>If this wasn't you, we recommend you secure your account
					immediately to prevent unauthorized access.</p>

				<p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
					<a href="{{link}}"
						style="background-color: #1a73e8; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
						Secure My Account
					</a>
				</p>

				<p>If you believe this is a mistake or need help, please contact the
					IT support team.</p>

				<p>Thank you,<br />
					<strong>IT Security Team</strong>
				</p>

				<hr style="margin-top: 40px; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;" />

				<p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888;">
					This message was sent by your organization's security monitoring
					system. Please do not reply directly to this email.
				</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</body>

</html>